{title: Transpose Demo}
{key: C}
{transpose: 2}

{comment: Original key C, transposed up 2 to D}

{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[C]Morning light on [F]fields of [G]gold
[Am]Stories waiting [F]to be [G]told
[C]Sing me something [F]warm and [G]true
[Am]Like the [F]sky is [G]always [C]blue
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_chorus}
[F]La la [C]la, [G]la la [Am]la
[F]La la [G]la la [C]la
{end_of_chorus}
